						<summary>

						<p>Fragments in four pieces contains the names of village and territorial divisions such as Mayipālakulakālapperunderu, Sōlakulavallinallūr, Sōmaṅgalam, Maṇaṟpākkuḍi, Dāmar-nāḍu and kōṭṭam in [Jayaṅ]goṇḍasōḻa-maṇḍalam, Pākkai-nāḍu in Gangaikoṇdasōḻa-vaḷanāḍu, other details are lost.</p>						

